             , she was a very ill Woman, and accused him out of spite, because they had borrow'd some Money and jointly given a Note for it, and she would have had her Name scratcht out of the Note, which because she did not get done, she threatned to be revenged on him. He called Evidencs to prove several of these Circumstances and also called several Persons to his Reputation. The Jury considering the matter <rs id="t17181015-29-verdict145" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17181015-29-verdict145" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
